<br>
Alright, this is the character thread for the RoTK rp.  This is not like the game, but it is more similar to Dynasty Warriors in a way.  But the rules of the forum are as stands so please follow them.  <br>
<br>
1.  You may not create a character who is invincible IOW A guy clad in armor that weight 300 pounds total running at the speed of a skinny dude in no armor at all.<br>
<br>
2.  2 character limit!  But if your character dies, you may create a new one.  But if the character dies within a certain thread, they may not return to the thread.   <br>
<br>
3.  Keep profanity to a minimum, unless your character has a problem with the other.  <br>
<br>
4.  Have Fun (put the General RP rules here as well.)<br>
<br>
Alrighty, this is how the character profiles will go then.<br>
<br>
Name:<br>
Age:<br>
Gender:<br>
Height/Weight:<br>
